98-3204 (La. 4/23/99)

STATE ex rel. Marlon Percy BRAMWELL v. STATE of Louisiana. No. 98-KH-3204. Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 23, 1999.

IN RE: Bramwell, Marlon Percy;— Plaintiff(s); Applying for Supervisory and/or Remedial Writs; Parish of Ouachita 4th Judicial District Court Div. “C” Number 48,831; to the Court of Appeal, Second Circuit, Number 31901-KH

Denied. La.C.Cr.P. art. 930.8; State ex rel. Glover v. State, 93-2330 (La.9/5/95), *877660 So.2d 1189; cf. La.C.Cr.P. art. 930.4(D).

VICTORY, J. not on panel.
